control_attributes.control_description: The information system: a. Prevents further access to the system by initiating a session lock after [Assignment: organization-defined time period] of inactivity or upon receiving a request from a user; andb. Retains the session lock until the user reestablishes access using established identification and authentication procedures.
control_attributes.Control_description: The information system implements [Assignment: organization-defined techniques or technologies] with [Assignment: organization-defined level of assurance] in associating security attributes to information.
